<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Plurity170</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f0f;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      padding: 24px 16px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #bbbbbb;
    }

    main {
      padding: 20px 16px;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    section p {
      color: #cccccc;
    }

    .card {
      background: #161616;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #222;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Plurity170</h1>
    <p>Building, learning, and sharing one step at a time.</p>
  </header>

  <main>

    <section>
      <h2>About</h2>
      <div class="card">
        <p>
          Welcome to my personal page. This space is for experiments,
          learning projects, and ideas as I grow in tech and creativity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <div class="card">
        <p>
          Projects will appear here soon. Stay tuned.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <div class="card">
        <p>
          You can connect with me on GitHub and other platforms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Plurity170 · Hosted on GitHub Pages
  </footer>

</body>
</html>